including websites, apps and rewards programs focused on luxury. 
 
He is highly experienced in digital product development and roll-out, and has been at the forefront of rolling 
out tech solutions for luxury clients from online advertising, mobile marketing to data systems. His track record 
includes signing up hundreds of luxury brands often for their very first forays into that technology. 
 
