Ultima card, as well as creating luxury rewards programs for Chinese banks and their credit cards. For the 
past 3 years, he has been Co-Founder and CEO of SERA, a rewards program in partnership with Visa China. 
SERA has acquired rewards from >100 luxury brand stores to date.  
 
Julian is an active investor in cryptocurrencies, and is concurrently a shareholder of Heart Media, owner of 
Singapore RendezVous, Phuket RendezVous and Penang RendezVous as well as multiple magazines and 
